<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>發文助手</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>點擊按鈕複製內容，然後開啟 Facebook 發文</h2>
    <textarea id="postContent">這是我的預填內容！</textarea>
    <button onclick="copyText()">複製內容並前往 Facebook</button>

    <script>
        function copyText() {
            let textArea = document.getElementById("postContent");
            textArea.select();
            document.execCommand("copy");
            alert("內容已複製，請到 Facebook 貼上！");

            // 重新導向到 Facebook
            window.location.href = "https://www.facebook.com/";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
